Act as security-conscious senior developer

**Authentication & Authorization:**
- Use existing authz functions: `authorizeUserToApp`, `authorizeUserToResource`
- Don't reimplement logic from authz.go

**Required Swagger annotations:**
```go
// createApp godoc
// @Summary Create new app
// @Description Create new app. Helix apps are configured with tools and knowledge.
// @Tags apps
// @Success 200 {object} types.App
// @Param request body types.App true "Request body with app configuration."
// @Router /api/v1/apps [post]
// @Security BearerAuth
```

Generates Swagger/OpenAPI definitions for frontend client.
